        "description": {
          "content": "Query the BDS time series. Use `YEAR` in the `get` clause and add it to\nthe `for` clause or filter with `time`, `STATE`, `MSA`, `NAICS`, `SECTOR`,\n`EAGE`, `FAGE`, `EMPSZES`, `FSIZE`, and other dimension variables.\n",
          "type": "text/plain"
        },
